content.html: Yesterday I got back from a 5-day @sourcegraph company meetup in Spain. I'm still in awe at how amazingly well-organized and produced it's been. Talks and production quality was higher than *a lot* of conferences I've been to in the past. Really cool.

Yesterday I got back from a 5-day @sourcegraph company meetup in Spain.

I'm still in awe at how amazingly well-organized and produced it's been.

Talks and production quality was higher than *a lot* of conferences I've been to in the past. Really cool.
